<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>* * *<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَمَنْ تَرَكَ رُكْناً فَذَكَرَهُ بَعْدَ شُرُوعِهِ فِي قِرَاءَةِ رَكْعَةٍ أُخْرَى:</span> بَطَلَتِ الَّتِي تَرَكَهُ مِنْهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَبْلَهُ:</span> يَعُودُ وُجُوباً، فَيَأْتِي بِهِ وَبِمَا بَعْدَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَإِنْ عَلِمَ بَعْدَ السَّلَامِ:</span> فَكَتَرْكِ رَكْعَةٍ كَامِلَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَإِنْ نَسِيَ التَّشَهُّدَ الأَوَّلَ وَنَهَضَ:</span> لَزِمَهُ الرُّجُوعُ مَا لَمْ يَنْتَصِبْ قَائِماً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">فَإِنِ اسْتَتَمَّ قَائِمًا:</span> كُرِهَ رُجُوعُهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَإِنْ لَمْ يَنْتَصِبْ:</span> لَزِمَهُ الرُّجُوعُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَإِنْ شَرَعَ فِي القِرَاءَةِ:</span> حَرُمَ الرُّجُوعُ، وَعَلَيْهِ السُّجُودُ لِلْكُلِّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>